LOCATION:UC Davis\, One Shields Ave\, Davis\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/a_WholeEarth-e1682549880754.jpg
END:VEVENT
