SUMMARY:Yoga Night at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Yoga & Wine at the Vineyard in Davis \n Second Wednesday of Each Month | 6:00–8:00PM May 13 | 6–8pm \nBack by popular demand\, FIT4MOM Davis-Woodland and Great Bear Vineyards are teaming up once again for the ultimate midweek reset—yoga\, wine\, and vineyard vibes. \nUnroll your mat and enjoy an easy to moderate Vinyasa flow led by the talented FIT4MOM Davis-Woodland instructors. Set to groovy tunes and tailored to your skill level\, this class is perfect whether you’re a seasoned yogi or just getting started.\nAs practice winds down\, you’ll be guided through an original inspirational meditation before settling in to enjoy a glass of delicious Great Bear wine.\n Ticket Includes: Yoga Class First Glass of Wine\nAfter class\, linger a little longer—take a stroll through the lavender fields\, set up a picnic\, or relax and socialize with new and old friends.\n A workout and wine are the stuff summer dreams are made of.\n What to Bring:• Yoga mat• Towel• Water• Money/card for an extra glass or bottle of wine• Picnic snacks or dinner items• Light jacket or sweater\n Organizer: FIT4MOM Davis-Woodland\nWe can’t wait to flow\, sip\, and unwind with you under the evening sky!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/yoga-night-at-great-bear-vineyards-2/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
