SUMMARY:The Sidekicks and Soul Ona Roll
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck at the Vineyard in Davis \n Friday\, May 15 | 5–8pm\nKick off your weekend with a relaxed evening of great wine\, live music\, and bold\, flavorful bites at the vineyard. \nJoin us for a laid-back night featuring live music from local favorites The Sidekicks and delicious Cajun & Creole-inspired comfort food from Soul Ona Roll. Sip your favorite estate-grown wines\, take in the vineyard views\, and enjoy an easygoing atmosphere with friends old and new.\n Ticket Includes: Glass of Wine Live Music\n Evening Schedule: Food Truck Serving: 5–8pm Live Music Performance: 6–7:30pm\n Music by The SidekicksWe’re thrilled to welcome back Marty Cohen & The Sidekicks—one of Northern California’s premier acoustic vocal groups. Featuring Marty Cohen\, Ken Rabiroff\, and Jeff Sears\, their rich 3-part harmonies and distinctive arrangements create a sound described as “urban folk with a pop twist.”\n Food Truck: Soul Ona RollCome hungry! Soul Ona Roll will be serving up mouthwatering Cajun and Creole-inspired classics\, including fan favorites like their famous Voodoo Fries. Please support this wonderful local business—no outside food permitted.\n Great wine\, soulful music\, and unforgettable flavors… the perfect Friday night pairing.\nGrab your tickets and join us at the vineyard!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/the-sidekicks-and-soul-ona-roll/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
