SUMMARY:Donut and Wine Pairing
DESCRIPTION:Donut & Wine Paired Tasting in Davis \n Saturday\, May 16 | 12–5pm\nDonuts + wine? Trust us… it’s a pairing you never knew you needed. \nWe’ve done the delicious research\, and the results are surprisingly sophisticated\, outrageously tasty\, and seriously fun. Join us at the vineyard for a playful tasting experience that celebrates unexpected flavor combinations and the joy of discovering your new favorite pairing.\n Ticket Includes: Flight of 4 Wines 4 Whole Donuts Paired to Match\n Suggested Pairings Include: Sparkling Brut or Mimosa + Classic Glazed Sparkling Rosé + Cherry or Red Jelly White Dessert Wine + Lemon\, Coconut\, or Maple Ruby Port-Style Dessert Wine + Chocolate or Maple\nEnjoy a guided tasting flight with pairing recommendations\, then mix\, match\, and experiment to discover your own perfect combinations. At the end\, cast your vote for the pairing that surprised you most!\nFeeling generous? Share the experience with friends by splitting donut pairings and adding separate wine tastings for additional guests ($20 per person).\n Bring your sweet tooth\, your curiosity\, and your favorite people for an afternoon filled with laughter\, indulgence\, and vineyard fun.\n Important Details:• Tickets must be purchased in advance• Ticket sales close Thursday\, May 14 at 12:00pm• Limited availability to ensure a relaxed\, high-quality experience\n Sweet treats\, sparkling wine\, and vineyard views? Count us in.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/donut-and-wine-pairing-2/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
